The Delves: Foes of the Free People
Foes of the Free Peoples found at East-delf and the West-delf should be defeated in order protect those within the Wildwood.

Foes can be found at the East-delf and West-delf in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should defeat foes at the East-delf and West-delf.
Foes of the Free Peoples have claimed the mining entrances of the East-delf and the West-delf within the Wildwood. Defeating their numbers here will assist in returning safety to the Wildwood.
